snippet.title: Minotaur Early Access trailer
snippet.description:
Minotaur is an adventure game about... Wait, why read about it here when you can watch our new Early Access trailer? Coming real soon to your nearest digital store.

Speaking of stores and money, if you liked what you see (and I hope that you did), don't forget to wishlist us on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/680590/Minotaur/

Thank you for watching! 💖🐧
